description: Goodbye is one of the first words people learn in a new language, which goes to show how often it is used. Considering this, I had to put together a section just for this farewell, which is said as either “bye,” “bye bye,” or “see you.” Writing “bye” twice comes off as a little cuter than if you just say it once.
